o 1 &Return "track 1
o 2 &Return "track 2
ma "marker a
2l mb "marker b
`a "move to marker a
v5l mc "create a visual region c at 5 lines
l 'a "select track 2 via mark a
Vk "also select track 1
~a "re-select only track 2 via timeline selection
V 0 "move to project start and remove selection
10l vh md "create a visual region c
&ctrl+apostrophe d "remove selection, delete mark d
